      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REVVED UP (1) was out of the placings when fifth last time but prior to that produced a superb 19.64 win over 350m at Goulburn. Has the ability and looks hard to top. CALYPSO ETHICS (2) was below best at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth at Wentworth Park, but was among the placings at this track three back. Can feature with the right run. SHREWD ETHICS (8) goes very well this course and distance starting 26 times for nine wins and nine minors. Placed last time (19.37) at this track in a NG, finishing third and beaten 4.5 lengths. Looks well placed here and among the chances. SCOTT WEDNESDAY (5) cannot be ruled out.",
